messages.message:
@Paul H `version-history` is failing because the app version is already shared, so the first click on the "Shared" radio button doesn't change anything, so the "Save" button stays disabled

should we manually set the app version to "Private" via an API call in the `before` block so that the app always starts in the expected state?
